This contain instruction for building glffmpeg on CentOS / Enterprise Linux 7

* Building glffmpeg with G++: 

  Requirements: 
  * GCC C++ compilers
    yum install gcc-c++
  * Make
    yum install make
  * OpenGL and GLU headers
    yum install mesa-libGL-devel mesa-libGLU-devel
  * ffmpeg 3.3.3 libraries and headers http://ffmpeg.zeranoe.com/builds/
  
  Build steps:
  * Update the ffmmpeg source directory within Makefile.config
  * Run make
  
